
NAME 
    scroll - a tool for viewing files

SYNOPSIS
    scroll [filename]

DESCRIPTION
    the scroll function creates an easy way to view .txt files
    either by page, or to scroll through at a set pace.

USE
    controls: SPACE- pan through pages
              ENTER- toggle scroll on/off
              F key- increase scroll speed
              S key- decrease scroll speed
              q key- quit program

AUTHOR
    Nicholas Drummey
